        <mxCell id="outputs-header" value="Three audiences. One artifact." style="text;html=1;fontSize=22;fontStyle=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontColor=#E5E7EB;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="495" width="1640" height="30" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="pitch-aud-1" value="&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:11px;color:#526C96;letter-spacing:2px;&#x27;&gt;FOR INVESTORS &amp;amp; RECRUITERS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&#x27;font-size:17px;color:#1E2933;&#x27;&gt;Why people stay — and why it can&amp;#x27;t be copied&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:12px;color:#3A4555;&#x27;&gt;Privacy-as-product.&lt;br&gt;Narrower tracking than every incumbent, full visibility into every learned row, autonomous alerting that gets sharper with use — a network-effect-free retention curve that compounds quietly per user.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:12px;color:#526C96;font-style:italic;&#x27;&gt;“I get the wedge in 30 seconds.”&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E5EEFD;strokeColor=#89B4FA;strokeWidth=2;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;shadow=1;arcSize=8;spacing=15;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="540" width="520" height="220" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="pitch-aud-2" value="&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:11px;color:#638860;letter-spacing:2px;&#x27;&gt;FOR ENGINEERS &amp;amp; COLLABORATORS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&#x27;font-size:17px;color:#1E2933;&#x27;&gt;How the system is built — top to bottom&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:12px;color:#3A4555;&#x27;&gt;Native Expo app is the daily surface; PWA stays for billing + auth-handoff.&lt;br&gt;Apple Foundation Models / Gemini Nano on-device, Vertex AI as the cloud floor.&lt;br&gt;30s server batch keeps cost predictable. Patterns mined nightly, not per-note.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:12px;color:#638860;font-style:italic;&#x27;&gt;“I can read this stack in one diagram.”&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#EBF8EA;strokeColor=#A6E3A1;strokeWidth=2;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;shadow=1;arcSize=8;spacing=15;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="590" y="540" width="520" height="220" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="pitch-aud-3" value="&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:11px;color:#796394;letter-spacing:2px;&#x27;&gt;FOR NON-TECHNICAL AUDIENCES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b style=&#x27;font-size:17px;color:#1E2933;&#x27;&gt;What it feels like to use&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:12px;color:#3A4555;&#x27;&gt;No daily-digest spam. No notifications until something actually matters.&lt;br&gt;Forgetting is allowed — the system remembers, the right way, at the right time, and gets noticeably sharper after the first month.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:12px;color:#796394;font-style:italic;&#x27;&gt;“It feels like an assistant who knows me.”&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F3EBFD;strokeColor=#CBA6F7;strokeWidth=2;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;shadow=1;arcSize=8;spacing=15;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="1150" y="540" width="520" height="220" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
        <mxCell id="bet-footer" value="&lt;b style=&#x27;color:#3F5566;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:11px;&#x27;&gt;THE BET&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&#x27;font-size:14px;color:#3A4555;&#x27;&gt;What makes NoteXT hard to copy isn&amp;#x27;t the AI — it&amp;#x27;s that the app learns less than competitors and shows you everything it learned.&lt;br&gt;That&amp;#x27;s why people stay. The reminders get sharper every week, and nobody else can build that without starting over.&lt;/span&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F4F6FA;strokeColor=#A8B3C2;dashed=1;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=14;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;shadow=1;arcSize=8;" parent="1" vertex="1"><mxGeometry x="160" y="800" width="1380" height="80" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
</mxfile>
